The ping/config/ping directory contains single node configuration
 of the ping society. 

MiniPing.xml is a basic defination with agent mobility enabled
MiniPing-metric.xml is a full throttle single-ping with the metric
  service loaded

To run MiniPing 
cd $CIP/ping/config/ping
$CIP/bin/Node MiniPing.xml NodeA
or
$CIP/bin/Node MiniPing-Metrics.xml NODE1
